    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This taxi is a time machine.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras/0f6f781a49959829761cc110a73db0db.avif?t=1759417062\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras_big/0f6f781a49959829761cc110a73db0db.avif?t=1759417062 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a taxi driver in a lunar city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your passengers and bring them to the time they truly desire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆The news is rewritten by the results of your chosen time travel.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras/a55147c2773492993ab0c626c457722c.avif?t=1759417062\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras_big/a55147c2773492993ab0c626c457722c.avif?t=1759417062 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you deliver a passenger to the past or the future,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >history is rewritten and news headlines change.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each passenger holds the fate of the world in his or her hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras/e11931a3ee3f735bcd84ad4ba2cba2be.avif?t=1759417062\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras_big/e11931a3ee3f735bcd84ad4ba2cba2be.avif?t=1759417062 width=800 height=578 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...Because every passenger is a &quot;suspect in a presidential assassination.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A series of choices creates a time paradox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything depends on your driving.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras/32504354d851014f48607a95a591153c.avif?t=1759417062\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305750/extras_big/32504354d851014f48607a95a591153c.avif?t=1759417062 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 100,000-character visual novel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nostalgic pixel art animation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parameters that are affected by your choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
